stood. Unbuckled his belt. She watched from the bed, still trembling, and told herself to stay clinical. Stay detached. He pushed his trousers down and his cock sprang free — thick, hard, the head flushed dark and already leaking. The kind of hard that made her mouth go dry. The kind that made her wonder how he&#39;d ever fit inside her.</p><p>He rolled a condom on. She watched his hands — steady, controlled, the hands of a man who&#39;d done this before and knew exactly what he was doing.</p><p>He came back to the bed. Hooked his fingers in her underwear and pulled it down her legs slowly, his eyes on hers the whole time. Settled between her thighs. His cock pressed against her — hot, hard, slick with the condom — and she wrapped her legs around him without thinking, her heels pressing into the small of her back, pulling him closer.</p><p>He pushed in slowly.</p><p>The stretch of him filling her made her gasp. He was thick — thicker than she&#39;d expected — and the fullness of it was almost too much. He paused when he was fully inside her, his forehead pressed against hers, his breath ragged against her mouth. She could feel him throbbing inside her, feel her body stretching to accommodate him, and the ache of it was so good she almost came from that alone.</p>",
